/shrug<br>
<br>
It was a surprise to me too.  The group tank said &quot;Hey your pet isnt BSing anymore.&quot;  I turn others hits on and sure enough, Jobober isn't BSing.<br>
<br>
I had equipped 62 waterpet with both 2 Blade of Walnan and 2 Fist of Ixiblat to test.  He no longer backstabbed.  At all.<br>
<br>
I then gave him a Dagger of Symbols and he equipped it in main hand, overwriting the Blade/Fist in that hand.  Backstabs returned.<br>
<br>
Don't ask me why it works like this now when it never did on old rogue pets, but it is this way with the new summoned weapons.<br>
<br>
Try it yourself.<br>
<br>
They should have made Blade of Walnan a Dagger of Walnan instead, so we could have slash, HTH, and piercing pets.<br>
